    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Questa manuelgerardi sp. n. SEM micrographs: A. Anterior end, lateral view; B. Anterior end, ventral view with buccal pad; C. Chaetigers, middle region; D. Posterior end, dorsal view. Abbreviations: bh, bidentate hook, cc capillary pinnate chaeta, ch1 chaetiger 1, ch5 chaetiger 5, mo mouth, no nuchal organ, nr neurochaeta, nt notochaeta, pa parapodium, pc pygidial cirri, pe peristomium, pr prostomium, py pygidium." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8203014/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8203016>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Questa manuelgerardi sp. n. SEM micrographs: A. Capillary pinnate chaeta; B. Chaetal bundle, bidentate hooks and capillary chaetae; C. Bidentate hook; D. Posterior end, lateral view. Abbreviations: at apical tooth, lg subdental ligament, mt main tooth." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8203016/files/figure.png" ;
